        "Title": "[Legion Co.] Target 07 - Sharon Reed",
        "Location": "LOCATION_WET_RAT",
        "PublicId": "130624857413",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/wet/scene_rat_basic.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 006e46cf-afb8-47af-bd88-905d574c6e8b).Image",
        "Description": "47, we have a major issue. With the leadership of Legion Corporation dead, ownership fell into the lap of their secret Co-Owner,  Sharon Reed...   She is one of our people, and even worse she has 3 close allies with her.  She is the director of the I.C.A. Data Center in China.  High Command has given us permission to take them out, however we must do so as quiet as possible to avoid giving her a chance to destroy our data.   The whole facility will do her bidding, expect hostility from the staff",
